#. (itstool) path: info/desc
#: ../help/C/drag-and-drop.page:6
msgid "Drop files, file names or timestamps on Parlatype"
msgstr "Ispusti datoteke, imena datoteka ili vremenske oznake na Parlatype"

#. (itstool) path: page/title
#: ../help/C/drag-and-drop.page:14
msgid "Drag and Drop"
msgstr "Povuci i ispusti"

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: ../help/C/drag-and-drop.page:16
msgid "You can drop files, file names or timestamps on <app>Parlatype</app>’s window."
msgstr ""
"Ispusti datoteke, imena datoteka ili vremenske oznake u <app>Parlatype</app> "
"prozor."

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: ../help/C/drag-and-drop.page:19
msgid "Files: Drag and drop a file from a file manager, e.g. <app>Files</app>, on <app>Parlatype</app> and it will open that file."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke: Povuci i ispusti datoteku iz upravljača datoteka, npr. <app>"
"Datoteke</app>, na <app>Parlatype</app> i ta će se datoteka otvoriti."

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: ../help/C/drag-and-drop.page:20
msgid "File names: Select a file name from a word processor, e.g. <app>LibreOffice</app>, drop the selected text on <app>Parlatype</app> and it will open that file. This will always work if the selection contains a full path. If you select the name only, <app>Parlatype</app> will look up its full path in the list of recent files and open it if it can find it in that list."
msgstr ""
"Imena datoteka: Odaberi ime datoteke u aplikaciji za obradu teksta, npr. "
"<app>LibreOffice</app>, ispusti odabrani tekst na <app>Parlatype</app> i ta "
"će se datoteka otvoriti. Ovo će uvijek funkcionirati ako odabir sadrži "
"potpunu stazu. Ako odabereš samo ime, <app>Parlatype</app> će pronaći "
"njegovu potpunu stazu u popisu nedavnih datoteka i otvoriti ga ako ga "
"pronađe u tom popisu."

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: ../help/C/drag-and-drop.page:21
msgid "Timestamps: You can drag and drop timestamps to <app>Parlatype</app>. Select a timestamp from a word processor, e.g. <app>LibreOffice</app>, drop the selected text on <app>Parlatype</app> and it will jump to that position."
msgstr ""
"Vremenske oznake: Vremenske oznake se mogu povući i ispustiti u <app>"
"Parlatype</app>. Odaberi vremensku oznaku iz aplikacje za obradu teksta, "
"npr. <app>LibreOffice</app>, ispusti odabrani tekst na <app>Parlatype</app> "
"i ona će skočiti na tu poziciju."

#. (itstool) path: info/desc
#: ../help/C/first-steps.page:7
msgid "First steps with Parlatype"
msgstr "Prvi koraci s Parlatypeom"

#. (itstool) path: page/title
#: ../help/C/first-steps.page:15
msgid "First Steps With Parlatype"
msgstr "Prvi koraci s Parlatypeom"

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: ../help/C/first-steps.page:17
msgid "<app>Parlatype</app> is an easy to use audio player to help you transcribing or annotating recorded speech. You need to run a word processor, e.g. <app>LibreOffice</app>, too. Launch <app>Parlatype</app> and open an audio file by clicking on the <gui>Open</gui> button in the upper left corner."
msgstr ""
"<app>Parlatype</app> je jednostavan audio player koji pomaže pri "
"transkripciji ili bilježenju snimljenog govora. Uz to moraš pokrenuti "
"aplikaciju za obradu teksta, npr. <app>LibreOffice</app>. Pokreni <app>"
"Parlatype</app> i otvori audio datoteku klikom na gumb <gui>Otvori</gui> u "
"gornjem lijevom kutu."

#. (itstool) path: note/p
#: ../help/C/first-steps.page:20
msgid "You can also drag and drop a file on <app>Parlatype</app>."
msgstr "Također možeš povući i ispustiti datoteku na <app>Parlatypeu</app>."

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: ../help/C/first-steps.page:23
msgid "In the lower left corner there are the controls with a <gui>Play</gui> button which toggles between play and pause. Whenever you pause, <app>Parlatype</app> rewinds a few seconds to make it easier to resume. This can be changed in the Preferences dialog."
msgstr ""
"U donjem lijevom kutu nalaze se kontrole s gumbom <gui>Pokreni</gui> za "
"mijenjanje između pokretanja i zaustavljanja snimke. Kada god zaustaviš "
"snimku, <app>Parlatype</app> je premotava nekoliko sekundi unatrag kako bi "
"ti bilo lakše nastaviti. Ovo se mož promijeniti u dijalogu „Postavke“."

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: ../help/C/first-steps.page:27
msgid "The buttons <gui>Skip backward</gui> and <gui>Skip forward</gui> in the lower left corner skip a few seconds back or ahead. The amount of time can be changed in the Preferences dialog."
msgstr ""
"Gumbovi <gui>Skoči natrag</gui> i <gui>Skoči naprijed</gui> u donjem lijevom "
"kutu preskaču nekoliko sekundi natrag ili naprijed. Vrijeme se može "
"promijeniti u dijalogu „Postavke“."

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: ../help/C/first-steps.page:29
msgid "The view scrolls automatically so that the cursor is always visible. You can scroll manually by clicking on or dragging the scroll bar or using the standard keybindings. Automatic scrolling is stopped then."
msgstr ""
"Prikaz se automatski pomiče tako da je kursor uvijek vidljiv. Možeš se ručno "
"pomicati klikom ili povlačenjem klizne trake ili korištenjem standardnih "
"tipki. Automatsko pomicanje se tada prekida."

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: ../help/C/first-steps.page:31
msgid "To get back to the cursor’s position and let the view scroll automatically again, click on the menu button showing the time and then on <gui>Go to Cursor</gui>. Clicking on the <gui>Play</gui> button also turns automatic scrolling on."
msgstr ""
"Za vraćanje na položaj kursora i ponovo aktiviranje automatskog pomicanja "
"prikaza, klikni na gumb izbornika koji prikazuje vrijeme, a zatim na <gui>"
"Idi na kursor</gui>. Klikom na gumb <gui>Pokreni</gui> također uključuje "
"automatsko pomicanje."

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: ../help/C/first-steps.page:33
msgid "Clicking in the view with the right mouse button will put the cursor there. The left mouse button is for <link xref=\"selections\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Klik desnom tipkom miša u prikazu postavit će kursor na to mjesto. Lijeva "
"tipka miša služi za <link xref=\"selections\"/>."

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: ../help/C/first-steps.page:35
msgid "The <gui>speed scale</gui> next to the <gui>Volume</gui> button in the lower right corner lets you adjust the speed of playback. A value of 1 means normal speed, everything lower (down to 0.5) is slower, everything above is faster."
msgstr ""
"<gui>Skala brzine</gui> pored gumba <gui>Glasnoća</gui> u donjem desnom kutu "
"omogućuje podešavanje brzine reprodukcije. Vrijednost 1 je normalna brzina, "
"sve manje vrijednosti (do 0,5) usporavaju, a sve veće ubrzavaju reprodukciju."

