#. (itstool) path: page/title
#: ../help/C/selections.page:14
msgid "Selections"
msgstr "Odabiri"

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: ../help/C/selections.page:16
msgid "You can select a piece of the waveform with the mouse. Next time you press <gui>Play</gui>, it will play the selection only. When it is finished and you press <gui>Play</gui> again, it will loop the selection once."
msgstr ""
"Dio valnog oblika zvuka možeš odabrati mišem. Sljedeći put kada pritisneš "
"<gui>Pokreni</gui> prikazat će se samo odabir. Kada završiš i ponovo "
"pritisneš <gui>Pokreni</gui>, odabir će se jednom ponoviti."

#. (itstool) path: note/p
#: ../help/C/selections.page:18
msgid "When in selection mode, you can not exit the selection anymore until you deselect it."
msgstr "U modusu odabira više ne možeš izaći iz odabira sve dok ga ne odznačiš."

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: ../help/C/selections.page:20
msgid "Selections can be made with the mouse (or pointer device) with a left click, holding the mouse button and dragging the pointer. If you click with <key>Shift</key> key pressed, an already existing selection will be enlarged to that point."
msgstr ""
"Odabiri se mogu napraviti mišem (ili pokazivačem) lijevim klikom, držanjem "
"tipke miša i povlačenjem pokazivača. Ako klikneš tipkom <key>Shift</key>, "
"već postojeći odabir će se povećati na tu točku."

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: ../help/C/selections.page:22
msgid "To deselect click once with the left button into the waveform. If the waveform has keyboard focus, you can press <key>Escape</key>."
msgstr ""
"Za poništavanje odabira klikni jednom lijevim gumbom u valni oblik zvuka. "
"Ako valni oblik zvuka ima fokus tipkovnice, možeš pritisnuti tipku <key>"
"Escape</key>."

