#: ../help/C/timestamps.page:14
msgid "Timestamps"
msgstr "Vremenske oznake"

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: ../help/C/timestamps.page:16
msgid "Timestamps help you to navigate in your transcription."
msgstr "Vremenske oznake pomažu pri navigaciji u transkripciji."

#. (itstool) path: note/p
#: ../help/C/timestamps.page:19
msgid "Timestamps can look like this: #03:45.2#. You can select them with or without the number signs."
msgstr ""
"Vremenske oznake mogu izgledati ovako: #03:45.2#. Mogu se prikazati sa ili "
"bez znakova za brojeve (#)."

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: ../help/C/timestamps.page:22
msgid "<app>Parlatype</app> can produce different timestamp formats, they can be set in the Preferences dialog."
msgstr ""
"<app>Parlatype</app> može proizvesti različite formate vremenskih oznaka. "
"One se mogu postaviti u dijalogu „Postavke“."

#. (itstool) path: section/title
#: ../help/C/timestamps.page:25
msgid "Drag and drop"
msgstr "Povuci i ispusti"

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: ../help/C/timestamps.page:27
msgid "If you select the timestamp in the word processor, you can drag and drop it on the <app>Parlatype</app> window and it will go to that position. This is also possible the other way round: Drag the time label from <app>Parlatype</app> to a word processor and drop it there to insert it."
msgstr ""
"Ako odabereš vremensku oznaku u programu za obradu teksta, možeš je povući i "
"ispustiti u <app>Parlatype</app> prozoru i ona će postaviti na tu poziciju. "
"To je moguće i obrnuto: povuci vremensku oznaku s <app>Parlatypea</app> u "
"program za obradu teksta i tamo je ispusti kako bi se umetnula."

#. (itstool) path: section/title
#: ../help/C/timestamps.page:31
msgid "Using the clipboard"
msgstr "Korištenje međuspremnika"

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: ../help/C/timestamps.page:33
msgid "Clicking on the menu button that is showing the current time you can <gui>Copy Time to Clipboard</gui> or <gui>Go to Time in Clipboard</gui>."
msgstr ""
"Klikom na gumb izbornika koji prikazuje trenutačno vrijeme omogućuje "
"koristiti opcije <gui>Kopiraj vrijeme u međuspremnik</gui> ili <gui>Idi na "
"vrijeme u međuspremniku</gui>."

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: ../help/C/timestamps.page:35
msgid "This can also be done with keyboard shortcuts. First make sure, the <app>Parlatype</app> window has focus. With the key sequence <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>c</key></keyseq> the current timestamp is copied to the clipboard. Changing to the word processor you can insert now the timestamp in your transcription."
msgstr ""
"To se može napraviti i pomoću tipkovnih prečaca. Najprije osiguraj da je "
"<app>Parlatype</app> prozor aktivan. Pomoću tipkovnog prečaca <keyseq><key>"
"Ctrl</key><key>c</key></keyseq>, trenutačna vremenska oznaka se kopira u "
"međuspremnik. Prelaskom na program za obradu teksta, sada možeš umetnuti "
"vremensku oznaku u svoju transkripciju."

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: ../help/C/timestamps.page:36
msgid "To go to a timestamp position, copy the timestamp in the word processor to the clipboard. Once you have changed focus to <app>Parlatype</app> press <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>v</key></keyseq>."
msgstr ""
"Za prijelaz na poziciju vremenske oznake, kopiraj vremensku oznaku u program "
"za obradu teksta u međuspremnik. Kada promijeniš fokus na <app>Parlatype</"
"app>, pritisni <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>v</key></keyseq>."
